---
GodMode sidebar pages outside the department tree: Home, Notifications, Calendar, Tasks, Bank, Vault, Support, Wiki, Structure (editors), Shared, Marketplace.

New workspaces start with an empty department tree. Users add departments via Intelligence or Structure once content exists.

Shared shows live resources granted by other users. Marketplace installs published packs into this workspace.
